    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sneak past the undead</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706170/extras/f215b1908287563a9b82eda91a8c85ef.poster.avif?t=1757579208\" width=332 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706170/extras/f215b1908287563a9b82eda91a8c85ef.webm?t=1757579208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706170/extras/f215b1908287563a9b82eda91a8c85ef.mp4?t=1757579208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The dead have risen from their graves and haunt this crypt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move past them without being seen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Teleport</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706170/extras/3ecd4804f40f7d320f0c1499fc883b33.poster.avif?t=1757579208\" width=332 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706170/extras/3ecd4804f40f7d320f0c1499fc883b33.webm?t=1757579208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706170/extras/3ecd4804f40f7d320f0c1499fc883b33.mp4?t=1757579208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You can't always just walk past the undead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place a teleport ahead of time and then teleport back to it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't get caught!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706170/extras/418c214e0043e91451ed7181fc9ed487.poster.avif?t=1757579208\" width=332 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706170/extras/418c214e0043e91451ed7181fc9ed487.webm?t=1757579208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706170/extras/418c214e0043e91451ed7181fc9ed487.mp4?t=1757579208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You're defenseless. Your only weapon is your wits and the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plan your moves</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706170/extras/21120fe7fce0dad87c780f07dd7d90e4.poster.avif?t=1757579208\" width=332 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706170/extras/21120fe7fce0dad87c780f07dd7d90e4.webm?t=1757579208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706170/extras/21120fe7fce0dad87c780f07dd7d90e4.mp4?t=1757579208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Dark Crypt is turn-based, you can take your time to plan and execute the moves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Dark Crypt?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A turn-based puzzler with a teleporting mechanic about sneaking through an ancient crypt, while avoiding its traps and the undead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The prophecy speaks of an ancient evil that slumbers within a crypt. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It foretells its awakening which will lead to our world being consumed by its dark shadow. Your brothers at the monastery dismiss it as a pagan heresy, however you know better than that.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world's fate rests on your shoulders. It's up to you to find the slumbering evil and seal it, before it awakens. Can you save our world?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What awaits you</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60 challenging levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss fights </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thinking with teleports </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinite undos </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skeletons, Vampires, Spikes and more! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro-rendition of chill-inducing classical music </p></li></ul>",
